game.name: My Cute Dog Bathing
game.description:
One of your friends carries a cute dog and she loves taking care of it on her own. Today her pet slipped and got dirty when she took him with her on the morning walk. Oh no! Your best friend also had an injury. So she has asked help from you. Can you help her giving his pet a friendly bath? Join My Cute Dog Bathing and be prepared to provide this cute dog with proper bathing and then dressing him up! Just follow the instructions to complete task as fast as you can!

Look at his face and we are damn sure that you cannot say no to help him! First of all, use water to rinse him up and apply a special pet shampoo and brush to wash him up properly! Make sure to dry his fur with the help of a blow dryer in this new girls game. He will again start looking nice when you use a new brush to pull all his fur all back in its place. In the next step, you have to clip his nails. 

Hey friends! You find him look neat and clean now. Once it is done, get ready to dress him up fast. Dress him up with some trendy outfits by browsing his wardrobe in this HTML5 animals name! Give him a sailor shirt, a cute saddle-like top with a panda bear or a denim vest! Make sure to give your pet a lovely funny hat along with a pair of cool sunglasses. Hope you would have a great time ahead with our more popular titles from the category of cute girls games!
